DATA SERVER
-----------

IP
172.27.47.111 for ssh
192.168.1.101 for nfs io

Login info
username: rocky
password: rocky

Anvil mount point
/mnt/nfs

Fuse mount point
/mnt/fuse

Run fuse daemon
sudo /home/rocky/demo/bin/run_pushdown_srvr_needs_sudo.sh

Fuse log
/tmp/fuse.log

Umount fuse
sudo umount /mnt/fuse

gRPC server log
/tmp/srvr-<pid>.log

Find and kill gRPC server
ps aux | grep 'pushdown-srvr/src/srvr.py'
kill -9 <pid>

Export fuse
sudo vim /etc/exports
sudo exportfs -a

Unexport fuse
sudo vim /etc/exports
sudo exportfs -r


