----------------
RESTART SEQUENCE
----------------

Client node:
1. kill vtk
2. kill presto
3. umount fuse

Data server node:
4. unexport fuse
5. umount fuse
6. find and kill grpc servers if there is any
7. mount fuse
8. export fuse

Client node:
9. mount fuse
10. start presto
11. start vtk
